{"id":"chatterbox-voice-clone","revision":0,"last_node_id":5,"last_link_id":4,"nodes":[{"id":3,"type":"PreviewAudio","pos":[1020,150],"size":[300,88],"flags":{},"order":3,"mode":0,"inputs":[{"localized_name":"audio","name":"audio","type":"AUDIO","link":2},{"localized_name":"audioUI","name":"audioUI","type":"AUDIO_UI","widget":{"name":"audioUI"},"link":null}],"outputs":[],"properties":{"Node name for S&R":"PreviewAudio"},"widgets_values":[]},{"id":5,"type":"Note","pos":[138.440761257318,615.9651599540881],"size":[820,280],"flags":{},"order":0,"mode":0,"inputs":[],"outputs":[],"properties":{"text":""},"widgets_values":["CHATTERBOX TTS — VOICE CLONE WORKFLOW\n==============================================\n\nSTEP 1: Load your reference audio (5-15 sec, clean, no background noise).\nSTEP 2: Type your text in the Chatterbox TTS node.\nSTEP 3: Adjust settings and hit Queue Prompt.\n\nSETTINGS:\n- exaggeration (0.25-2.0): Controls emotion intensity.\n     0.25 = flat/monotone | 0.5 = natural | 1.0+ = very expressive\n- cfg_weight (0.2-1.0): Controls pace and guidance.\n     Lower = faster/looser | Higher = slower/more controlled\n- temperature (0.05-5.0): Controls randomness.\n     0.5 = stable | 0.8 = natural | 1.5+ = unpredictable\n- seed: Same seed + same text = same output. Change it for variations.\n- keep_model_loaded: Set to True to avoid reloading the model each run.\n\nTIP: For the Turbo model, you can add [laugh], [sigh], [gasp] in your text!"],"color":"#233","bgcolor":"#355"},{"id":1,"type":"LoadAudio","pos":[100,200],"size":[300,136],"flags":{},"order":1,"mode":0,"inputs":[{"localized_name":"audio","name":"audio","type":"COMBO","widget":{"name":"audio"},"link":null},{"localized_name":"audioUI","name":"audioUI","type":"AUDIO_UI","widget":{"name":"audioUI"},"link":null},{"localized_name":"choose file to upload","name":"upload","type":"AUDIOUPLOAD","widget":{"name":"upload"},"link":null}],"outputs":[{"localized_name":"AUDIO","name":"AUDIO","type":"AUDIO","links":[